layed was one of the Final Fantasies on gameboy (haven't played it in years, not sure of name).  But all my guys had the best equipment and every kind of magic and were all maxxed level and I still got killed sooooo many times on the last boss.  And when I did kill him eventually it took me 30 minutes or so.  It was the best battle I had ever had in an RPG.<br><br>What happened to hard bosses?  I miss not being challenged anymore. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#E6E6FA><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub18.ezboard.com/uvlakoradosvlasher.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Vlakorados Vla Sher</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_fire.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>MithMarr Sentinel<BR><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/shellene/star.gif height=10 width=11 border=0><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/shellene/star.gif height=10 width=11 border=0><img src=http://pages.cthome.net/shellene/star.gif height=10 width=11 border=0></span><br>  Posts: 217<br> <font color=#4B0082>(1/28/02 5:53:40 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub18.ezboard.com/fmithanielmarrdailynewsfrm11.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=997.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://www.geocities.com/phinphanphorever/cane.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Last Bosses</span><hr size=1> Sephiroth was a bad ass. Really deep character. I think they should have made him tougher. I really hate the auto win last battle. <p><TABLE BORDER=0><TR><TD><A HREF="http://blog.ravenblack.net/quiz/videogame.pl"><IMG BORDER=0 ALIGN="LEFT" WIDTH=150 HEIGHT=80 SRC="http://blog.ravenblack.net/quiz/videogame/14.png" ALT="What Video Game Character Are You? I am a Gauntlet Adventurer." /></A>I am <B>a Gauntlet Adventurer</B>.<BR /><BR />I strive to improve my living conditions by hoarding gold, food, and sometimes keys and potions. I love adventure, fi